name: Toiletbread Gets Stuffed
description:
Use the directional keys or WASD on your keyboard to move Toiletbread's head around!

Toiletbread is HUNGRY! But, her head has separated from her body somehow so you'll have to slide her around so she can FEAST. Luckily some slob dropped a bunch of mcri- I mean pork-based rib sandwiches on the floor so, be sure to eat up!
It's only 1 level. Also, this was my first game in Unity and I used a tutorial so don't expect much Σ(;Φ ω Φ)

*Note: This was previously a download called Toiletbread- the Game, but I took that down, changed the BG in-game and made it playable on your browser so you don't have to fill your hard drive with nonsense! Thanks, Unity!
